import React from 'react'; import { Box, Typography, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Paper } from '@mui/material'; import { toWords } from 'number-to-words'; const FormComponentNMT = ({ rollNumber = 'NMT2023001', name = 'Student Name', sod = "Parent's Name", examDate = 'June 2025', subjectsData = [ { paperNo: 'I', subject: 'Anatomy, Physiology & Basic Chemistry, Physics and Maths', theoryMax: 100, theorySecured: 85, practicalMax: null, practicalSecured: null, totalMax: 100, totalSecured: 85, result: 'Pass' }, // Add other papers similarly ], specialty = 'Nuclear Medicine Technology' }) => { const borderStyle = '1px solid #ddd'; const headerBg = '#f5f5f5'; // Calculate grand total const grandTotal = subjectsData.reduce((total, subject) => total + (subject.totalSecured || 0), 0); const totalInWords = toWords(grandTotal).replace(/,/g, ' ').toUpperCase(); return ( {/* University Header */} Nizam's Institute of Medical Sciences (A University established under the State Act) PUNJAGUTTA: HYDERABAD - 500 082
TELANGANA STATE, INDIA {/* Document Title */} MEMORANDUM OF MARKS {/* Student Information */} Roll No: {rollNumber} Postgraduate Diploma in {specialty} First Year Final Examination held in the month of {examDate} Name: {name} S/O./D/O: {sod} {/* Marks Table */} Paper Subject Theory Practical/Viva Total Maximum Marks Marks Secured Maximum Marks Marks Secured Maximum Marks Marks Secured {subjectsData.map((subject, index) => ( {subject.paperNo} {subject.subject} {subject.theoryMax} {subject.theorySecured || '-'} {subject.practicalMax || 'NA'} {subject.practicalMax ? (subject.practicalSecured || '-') : 'NA'} {subject.totalMax} {subject.totalSecured || '-'} ))}
{/* Footer Information */} Aggregate marks in words: {totalInWords} Result: PASS Dated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-IN')}
EXECUTIVE REGISTRAR AP: Already Pass; AB: Absent; NA: Not applicable ); }; export default FormComponentNMT;
